 western regions due to more intense$\backslash$ncrop-management, greater soil erodibility, and more rainfall. The$\backslash$nrelationships between erosion parameters and the most important$\backslash$nvegetation attributes were also used to provide models with equations$\backslash$nthat were specific to the study region. The results of this paper can be$\backslash$nuseful for better understanding erosion processes at the micro-scale and$\backslash$nmacro-scale in any region having similar vegetation attributes to the$\backslash$nforests of northern Iran.},
