st under Argisol is essential to the conservation of this pedoenvironment, especially in steep slopes.},
author = {Bispo, Di{\^{e}}go Faustolo Alves and Silva, Marx Leandro Naves and Pontes, Lucas Mac Hado and Guimar{\~{a}}es, Danielle Vieira and {De S{\'{a}} E Melo Marques}, Jo{\~{a}}o Jos{\'{e}} Granate and Curi, Nilton},
